<h1>Catnipporium Supports Cat Cafes</h1>
<p>Here at Catnipporium, we love Cat Cafes! What a lovely place to grab a drink and chill out with some furballs :)<p>
<p>Here we aim to have the most <em>complete and accurate</em> listing of Cat Cafes around, and provide enough information to plan your visit! Check here for location, contact info, opening hours and price!<p>
{% for country, states in cafes_ordered %}
	<h3 class="title is-3">{{ country }}</h3>
	{% for state, cities in states | dictsort %}
		<h4 class="subtitle is-4 ml-1 mt-3 mb-0">{{ state }}</h4>
	  <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
		{% for city, cafes in cities |dictsort %}
				<div class="cafe-card">
				  <div class="cafe-inner">
				    <h3 class="cafe-city">{{ city }}</h3>
						<ul>
		        {% for cafe in cafes %}
				      <li><p class="cafe-name"><a href="/catcafes/{{ cafe | slugify }}/">{{ cafe }}</a></p></li>
            {% endfor%}
						</ul>
				  </div>
				</div>
		{% endfor %}
		</div>
	{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
